# Acceptance Criteria
The implementation is complete when:
* No analytics IDs are hardcoded anywhere in the project.
* All providers read configuration exclusively from the centralized configuration module.
* The application runs correctly in Local, Preview, and Production environments.
* Missing configuration disables only the affected provider without breaking the app.
* Analytics are initialized lazily and do not impact page load performance.
* Debug logging is available only when `NEXT_PUBLIC_ANALYTICS_DEBUG=true`.
* The codebase is clean, modular, type-safe, and ready to support additional analytics providers in the future.